  <div class="wrapper-content">
    <div class="full-up formatting">
      <h2>Validating Ideas</h2>
      <p>We prototyped and tested ideas to validate ideas quickly. Through collaborative effort with the MeetingHero product team we pushed the agile development process to it's limits. From start to finish there was an ongoing cycle of idea evaluation, prototyping, and user validation. New iterations were deployed near daily. Our continuous integration practice ensured that despite the pace our users could expect a solid user experience.</p>

      <p>Web app development has evolved to the point that it's  possible to rapidly prototype via assemblage. That is, piece together  each feature as if they were Legos. We started by assembling raw user flows with ready-made components to check assumptions. Since the intimacy of in-person meetings contributes to it's success, we used realtime technology to enable attendees to instantly collaborate on a meeting 'dashboard'. A dashboard is living documentation of a meeting that records thoughts, decisions and action items.</p>

      <h2>Hello Effective Meetings</h2>
      <p>MeetingHero is a collaborative meeting dashboard that provides the right amount of structure to add value to any type of meeting. Attendees can work together to direct the meeting in realtime and summaries are emailed to all parties when the meeting ends. It is synced via the cloud and seamlessly integrates with Google accounts.
</p>
